WEBVTT

1
00:08:47.390 --> 00:08:49.250 
你和你妻子为什么离婚
why did you and your wife split up?

2
00:08:49.250 --> 00:08:51.740 
你也知道的  我们的追求不一样
Oh, you know how it is-- we wanted different things.

3
00:08:51.740 --> 00:08:52.950 
我想要孩子
I wanted children,

4
00:08:52.950 --> 00:08:56.300 
她想要一个叫让·菲利普的糕点师
and she wanted a pastry chef named Jean-Philippe.

5
00:08:57.150 --> 00:08:58.780 
我深感同情
Oh, I'm... I'm so sorry.

6
00:08:58.780 --> 00:09:00.670 
没事的  我就是因此而离开英国
No, it's-it's fine. It's why I left England.

7
00:09:00.670 --> 00:09:02.510 
那里有太多事物会让我想起她
It reminded me too much of her.

8
00:09:02.510 --> 00:09:03.820 
冷冷的  闷闷的
Cold, gloomy

9
00:09:03.820 --> 00:09:07.660 
英国和法国之间有一条海底铁路隧道

10
00:09:03.820 --> 00:09:07.660 
随便让法国佬从"隧道"进入
and easily accessed by a Frenchman through a tunnel.

11
00:09:08.970 --> 00:09:11.110 
他们在哪里
Hey. So, where are they?

12
00:09:11.110 --> 00:09:13.370 
对面街的左边窗口
Across the street, in the left window.

13
00:09:13.820 --> 00:09:16.410 
靠  我们应该带望远镜来的
Oh, damn it, we should have brought binoculars.

14
00:09:16.410 --> 00:09:17.740 
早有准备
Right here.

